{"tid":2449293,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"如果非要在我對hoegaarden嘅愛加上一個期限，我希望係…一萬年","createTime":"2021-03-16T14:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T17:27:11.000Z","uid":258192,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee655f21866a7579bb93386839fb9e6a1c60872","tid":2449293,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"前幾日比frd捉去酒吧飲酒 本身覺得酒好撚難飲<br />\n但係為咗個frd 就陪佢去酒吧做wingman<br />\n去到酒吧我唔知叫咩好 個frd重玩鳩我叫我飲heineken<br />\n之前比佢水我飲heineken 難聽d講真係難飲個尿<br />\n又唔想比錢飲cocktail 唔通比錢買難受<br />\n<br />\n我個frd開始吹鳩我話叫我la la聲買杯野陪佢搵食<br />\n我個吓做咗我人生之中一個重要嘅決定<br />\n我鼓起勇氣同個bartender講 'Can I have a pint of Hoegaarden?'<br />\n我同個bartender四目相投<br />\n佢。。。向我展露無比堅定嘅眼神<br />\n佢嘅眼神話比我聽我係做咗一個明智嘅選擇<br />\n<br />\n當個pint Hoegaarden到我手嘅一刻<br />\n我即刻豪爽咁飲咗一啖<br />\n我。。。從來未飲過咁好飲嘅啤酒<br />\n個一刻 所有係bar到嘅靚女全部都比唔上呢杯啤酒<br />\n呢杯啤酒令我明白到人生嘅真蹄<br />\n望住我個frd每過幾個月就同條女散 然後又去bar搵食<br />\n相反 Hoegaarden可以無時無刻都係我身邊 默默陪我走過我每一個高山低谷<br />\n我希望我對hoegaarden嘅愛係&hellip;一萬年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Tl:dr Hoegaarden真係好撚好飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb48894906f27df7aea5fb2a5eba7c95184df50","tid":2449293,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"有冇angel ring?"},{"pid":"79115f910d9f0c7bc9b04680953555de429f8441","tid":2449293,"uid":103575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:23:42.000Z","msg":"試下paulaner"},{"pid":"97eb4d6c1bee08c218d0fb2ab0e4be7857981921","tid":2449293,"uid":62983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"Rosee?"},{"pid":"5e9844cd2f1c811b6074d5131d484015f64046a9","tid":2449293,"uid":344249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:29:30.000Z","msg":"建議你試埋d德國啤酒先<br />\n超市買到既erdinger paulaner都好過hoegaarden<br />\n再好飲d但難買d既有franziskaner maisel's weisse"},{"pid":"afdaf88d0057de491114c212fdc514a820f459b4","tid":2449293,"uid":293943,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:31:34.000Z","msg":"Hoegaarden都話好飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0782c0a16badf7a85fb5d7c449900d33498e4a4","tid":2449293,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5bb48894906f27df7aea5fb2a5eba7c95184df50","tid":2449293,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"有冇angel ring?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:32:03.000Z","msg":"無留意 係咪一定要有angel ring先好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d6954a244b9bd56804cefa69933354cb364efb","tid":2449293,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"初嚐啤酒 各位ching屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216bc06df696860a932d1a338e3428ce0b18aaa4","tid":2449293,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afdaf88d0057de491114c212fdc514a820f459b4","tid":2449293,"uid":293943,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:31:34.000Z","msg":"Hoegaarden都話好飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:35:12.000Z","msg":"淡到咁不如飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2dcf440ed38725971fac33216ffa49d3b8c6e6","tid":2449293,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97eb4d6c1bee08c218d0fb2ab0e4be7857981921","tid":2449293,"uid":62983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"Rosee?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"Hoegaarden white"},{"pid":"0603b24018b910b06f7ec6aa357caab2d4cc297f","tid":2449293,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e9844cd2f1c811b6074d5131d484015f64046a9","tid"